channel.title: Uncalled Attack v5 - Time to Save Project Insanity
channel.description:
[center][img]http://img339.imageshack.us/img339/8832/uarise.jpg[/img][/center] Not the best banner ever, I know, but server developments aren't created for the banners.
This project is basically created for the new rise of Project Insanity. I'm here to help the horrible usage of Project Insanity servers, we all know how Project Insanity servers have gone to complete shit. With me behind the wheel, I'm here to fix errors of the poorly used source. I want this source to go down in history of the resurrection for Project Insanity sources. You might know of my previous development "Power to the People," I'm done with that development. That's beside the point, we don't want terrible sources corrupting our RuneScape developments, that's the reason for the creation of this source - wish me luck! [hr] [hr] [size=14pt][b]The Team:[/b][/size]
[ul][li]Uncalled[/li] [li]You'll find out soon enough[/li][/ul]
[hr] [hr] [code=Update Log] -Thursday, December 15 | Better woodcutting base -Thursday, December 15 | Better firemaking base -Thursday, December 15 | Clipped firemaking -Thursday, December 15 | Clipped following -Saturday, December 17 | Combat updated -Saturday, December 17 | Very small networking update -Saturday, December 17 | New Watchtower training teleport -Saturday, December 17 | Edited quite a bit to have a great economy -Saturday, December 17 | Much faster switching -Sunday, December 18 | Completed classes -Sunday, December 18 | Fixed the general store dupe, you can still buy & sell items there [/code] [hr] [hr] [size=14pt][b]Videos:[/b][/size] [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tbOQS5MUdAA[/youtube] [hr] [hr] [size=14pt][b]Pictures:[/b][/size] [img]http://img17.imageshack.us/img17/6538/uncalledattack201112152.png[/img] [img]http://img687.imageshack.us/img687/7979/uncalledattack201112171.png[/img]

item.title: Uncalled Attack v5 - Time to Save Project Insanity
item.dc:creator: @Loveandpower Loveandpower
item.description:
@Loveandpower wrote:

I told you I was pr0 beta tester ^.^

-pmed mining “bugs” to uncalled
-pmed shop dupe to uncalled
-crafting needs cutting anim (with proper anims or whatever for that specific gem)
-crafting gems makes the complete enchanted amulet instead of the regular amulet ( would be a great addition to make enchantments work wouldn’t be hard either )
-when you drop an item near the bottom of your inventory your interface changes (common bug but thought I would let you know )
-blow kiss does not show the red heart <3
-BABYMAKING SKILL IS NOT ADDED o wait…
-very easy to do but add the serba name to the logout interface/bank
-pm handlestatus “cough"delete that :“cough”
-i like noclipping xD
-ignore needs adding
-you can still pm a person even if they are not online (ofc message wont send but thought I would lte you know so you can make a message like " that person isn’t online idiot…”
-unequiped combat (-1 I think ? ) is incorrect attack,strength,defence
-i can join the same clan chat more than once xD(feel free to rip the clan chat fix from my source :o even though honestly it’s easy to fix )
-you cannot click the ore in your inventory then click on the furnace to make the bar
-smithing needs to be redone to be like runescape (where it takes coal as well etc)
-smelt x does not work
-smelt 10, 5 does not work

edit:

-you can smith without a hammer…
-you can smith way too fast
-smith 10 does not work

edit #2

-sometime around dspk this was fixed…but um there is this arrow glitch sort of hard to explain. something about you equip arrows and then you get some new arrows out of the bank, and then you unequip arrows and you have two different piles of the same arrow
-there are several duel arena dupes you can fix most by looking at R-S
-make it so it closes the stake interface after it resets the dueling options…so people can’t do the newest dupe
-make it so you have to logout before you can go to duel arena after going to tzhaar…the tzhaar/duel dupe fix ( well my fix for it )
-trade dupes
-cheat engine dupes
-wildy dupes
-that weird time when at barrows your minmaps effs up until relogin
-cant talk in public in current smithing area ( has something to do with that being the tutorial island )
-you position incorrectly away from the anvil when smithing
-there is no smelting anim or whatever

edit #3

-you can cut trees from a distance should be fixed so you have to be right by the tree.
-fires do not show
-you do not go one space to the left,right, north , or south when firemaking(obviously good old PI firemaking <3 )
-there is no animation when fletching(make sure to add the different id’s for each log , there is no animation either for shaft creation.
-you cant make arrows/bolts/darts would be a nice addition
-you can mass spam click the arrow shaft creation on the interface to make them
-arrow shaft making 5, 10, and x do not work
-tree respawn time is way off
-SOMETIMES the woodcutting animation just stops…even though a log or etc has not been given.
-sometimes you can click on a tree and it won’t start cutting…llike there is something wrong with positioning or something.
-correct me if I am wrong but every higher level log if you make shafts you can make more shafts?
-itemonitem for firemaking… you can firemake if you use the tinderbox on the log but not the other way around/easy fix to be honest.
-fishing spots do not move around
-…um im not really sure what is causing this ( maybe variables are not being reset?) but like you can click away from th fishing spot, go cook the shrimp go bank it etc and you will still be fishing shrimp
-shark xp , and the manta xp should be changed…
-you need a cook timer
-cooking interface needed (with working cook 1, 5, 10, x)

Read full topic
